Come hear what Jenn says she loved the most about the self paced, online teacher course all about Classroom Management.

✨ creating a student-run classroom that was a calm, positive place to learn isn’t just possible… it can be done WITHOUT frustration, overwhelm, and taking MORE time away from your teaching

😝Do you ever feel like no matter what you do for classroom management, you still…

👉🏼Seem to have constant interruptions?
👉🏼Spend more time getting your class on task than teaching?
👉🏼Feel like your class (or a particular group of students) runs the
classroom?

🥳With the right strategies and activities, you can get your students on board and start maximizing your teaching time! 

Join us before the doors close! Teachcreatemotivate.com/academy

Ten of my favorite Google Classroom tips to make it more engaging and effective for your students!⁣
⁣
I’ve loved Google Classroom for years, and anytime I post about it get lots of questions! ⁣
⁣
Whether you’re new to using GC or not maybe some of these tips can be helpful to you! 🥰⁣
⁣
Whats your favorite tip?! 👇🏼👇🏼👇🏼⁣
⁣
To read an extensive blog post that shares even more Google Classroom tips for use click the link in my bio! https://www.teachcreatemotivate.com/using-google-classroom/ #teachersofinstagram #teachersfollowteachers #iteach #iteachtoo
